{"tid":1395970,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真) 終於知道大陸人點解咁健康","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:20:12.000Z","uid":132461,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb666119e133559f5e899a80d7186672661516fe","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>Your Chair Is Killing You...Time To Start Squatting.</strong><br />\n<br />\nSitting Is Killing You Slowly<br />\n<br />\nYou'll probably be surprised at how much evidence there is out there that sitting is terrible for our bodies, and not just for our lower backs.  Studies have shown over and over that sitting long periods of the day (as we almost all do) has disastrous effects our cellular and metabolic health.<br />\n<br />\nOur Bodies Were Not Designed To Sit<br />\n<br />\nThe Solution: Squatting<br />\n<br />\nIn most traditional cultures around the world, lower back pain is almost non-existent, despite the fact that people living in these societies perform a lot more physical labor.<br />\n<br />\nThe reason for this is pretty clear-cut.  Most people in traditional societies rarely, if ever, sit in chairs for long periods of time.  If they need to rest, they squat.  Put simply, it's what our bodies are designed to do.  <br />\n<br />\nWhen we squat, our lumbar spine extends, stretching the muscles in our low-back.  There is little-to-no compression in the spine and stabilization is distributed between the muscles of the legs, hips and core.  It's a perfect posture. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://besynchro.com/blogs/blog/10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbesynchro.com%2Fblogs%2Fblog%2F10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=c1472fee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://besynchro.com/blogs/blog/10612681-your-chair-is-killing-you-time-to-start-squatting</a>"},{"pid":"26595aba5f8bfa6779ca526d29ca700eaebfdca9","tid":1395970,"uid":6294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"14c7187ac3da38e6108001a1ec17ab3c2561438c","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fb2a961024f73c303ed78bbad9e5aea44834b9b","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eb565be7237c5a6cbcf279a82b20b2ad0afed64","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c1e9b4b7c944eac17512a294434e6ce2487f7a4","tid":1395970,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得啱。 除左因為大陸人蹲個時通常都做埋D衰衰格格野， 蹲本身對身體係幾好架。"},{"pid":"4f702b691bb59c6132c1cdcf47f974c3c9a5bbb1","tid":1395970,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"蹲廁好似健康d嫁"},{"pid":"22431959ff389449b9d0d354ba20f357e33f92db","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7947318b679cec9858a2da78a31b203b88b8d94f","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb73f4e054ebe68c622a099caa5685d15d2eda29","tid":1395970,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:15:55.000Z","msg":"一早知 但屌你老母呢個姿勢點柯屎 成褲成鞋都係？"},{"pid":"d0e349626ff858288ffa27e10a5670b8ded2d005","tid":1395970,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:26:40.000Z","msg":"試下早晚蹲，每次三至五分鐘"},{"pid":"356b1db2a43b806b711a3443c16471e84bc5ca6d","tid":1395970,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit